msgid "Privacy note"
msgstr "Catatan privasi"

msgctxt "privacyNoteDescription"
msgid "The reference aggregate intentionally stays high level so it can be published publicly without revealing individual registry entities, verification events, or protected attributes."
msgstr "Agregat referensi ini sengaja tetap tingkat tinggi sehingga bisa dipublikasikan tanpa mengungkap entitas registry individual, event verifikasi, atau atribut yang dilindungi."

