msgctxt "heroTitle"
msgid "Build Anything on a Resilient Foundation"
msgstr "Bangun Apa Saja di Atas Fondasi yang Tangguh"

msgctxt "heroSubtitle"
msgid "AWCMS-Micro combines the absolute reliability of single-tenant architecture with the flexible extension model of EmDash. Fully integrated, zero core modifications, completely tenant-ready."
msgstr "AWCMS-Micro menggabungkan keandalan mutlak arsitektur single-tenant dengan model ekstensi EmDash yang fleksibel. Terintegrasi penuh, tanpa modifikasi core, siap untuk multi-tenant."

msgctxt "heroCtaPrimary"
msgid "Explore Admin"
msgstr "Jelajahi Admin"

msgctxt "heroCtaSecondary"
msgid "Read Documentation"
msgstr "Baca Dokumentasi"

msgctxt "featuresTitle"
msgid "Engineered for Every Use Case"
msgstr "Didesain untuk Segala Kebutuhan"

msgctxt "featuresSubtitle"
msgid "From standard marketing sites to complex data backends, AWCMS-Micro provides a unified development experience."
msgstr "Dari situs web pemasaran standar hingga backend data yang kompleks, AWCMS-Micro menyediakan pengalaman pengembangan yang terpadu."

msgctxt "featureCmsTitle"
msgid "Modern CMS"
msgstr "CMS Modern"

msgctxt "featureCmsDesc"
msgid "Flexible content structures for blogs, news, and pages with instant preview and publishing."
msgstr "Struktur konten fleksibel untuk blog, berita, dan halaman dengan pratinjau dan publikasi instan."

msgctxt "featureShopTitle"
msgid "E-Commerce Ready"
msgstr "Siap E-Commerce"

msgctxt "featureShopDesc"
msgid "Secure transactions, product galleries, and inventory management powered by custom microservices."
msgstr "Transaksi aman, galeri produk, dan manajemen inventaris yang didukung oleh microservices kustom."

msgctxt "featureAppTitle"
msgid "Custom Web Apps"
msgstr "Aplikasi Web Kustom"

msgctxt "featureAppDesc"
msgid "Robust APIs and serverless workflows to power tailored web portals and business applications."
msgstr "API tangguh dan alur kerja serverless untuk mendukung portal web kustom dan aplikasi bisnis."

msgctxt "featureAdminTitle"
msgid "Admin Center"
msgstr "Pusat Admin"

msgctxt "featureAdminDesc"
msgid "A complete, customizable backoffice portal for data entry, audits, and governance workflows."
msgstr "Portal backoffice lengkap yang dapat disesuaikan untuk entri data, audit, dan alur kerja tata kelola."

msgctxt "featureMobileTitle"
msgid "Mobile Backend"
msgstr "Backend Mobile"

msgctxt "featureMobileDesc"
msgid "Ultra-fast REST and GraphQL endpoints designed to feed native Android and iOS applications."
msgstr "Endpoint REST dan GraphQL super cepat yang dirancang untuk mendukung aplikasi native Android dan iOS."

msgctxt "featureIotAiTitle"
msgid "IoT & AI Integrations"
msgstr "Integrasi IoT & AI"

msgctxt "featureIotAiDesc"
msgid "Real-time sensor pipelines, agent webhooks, and AI model orchestration out of the box."
msgstr "Pipeline sensor real-time, webhook agen, dan orkestrasi model AI langsung dari kotak."

msgctxt "useCasesTitle"
msgid "Concrete Implementations"
msgstr "Implementasi Nyata"

msgctxt "useCasesSubtitle"
msgid "See how AWCMS-Micro templates and plugins adapt to your architectural demands."
msgstr "Lihat bagaimana template dan plugin AWCMS-Micro menyesuaikan dengan kebutuhan arsitektur Anda."

msgctxt "useCaseCmsHeading"
msgid "1. Headless Website CMS"
msgstr "1. CMS Website Headless"

msgctxt "useCaseCmsText"
msgid "Manage content with standard EmDash collections and deliver it statically or dynamically. Astro-powered frontend provides optimal load times and top-tier SEO performance."
msgstr "Kelola konten dengan koleksi EmDash standar dan sajikan secara statis atau dinamis. Frontend bertenaga Astro memberikan waktu muat optimal dan performa SEO terbaik."

msgctxt "useCaseShopHeading"
msgid "2. Secure E-Commerce"
msgstr "2. E-Commerce yang Aman"

msgctxt "useCaseShopText"
msgid "Implement product feeds, interactive search, and secure checkouts. Leverage Cloudflare KV or durable storage to build performant, globally-distributed storefronts."
msgstr "Implementasikan feed produk, pencarian interaktif, dan checkout aman. Manfaatkan Cloudflare KV atau penyimpanan tahan lama untuk membangun toko global berperforma tinggi."

msgctxt "useCaseAppHeading"
msgid "3. Enterprise Web Portals"
msgstr "3. Portal Web Perusahaan"

msgctxt "useCaseAppText"
msgid "Construct responsive layouts and workflows with full support for user authorization, settings, and third-party API integrations."
msgstr "Bangun tata letak dan alur kerja responsif dengan dukungan penuh untuk otorisasi pengguna, pengaturan, dan integrasi API pihak ketiga."

msgctxt "useCaseAdminHeading"
msgid "4. Multi-Tenant Admin Portals"
msgstr "4. Portal Admin Multi-Tenant"

msgctxt "useCaseAdminText"
msgid "AWCMS-Micro includes a powerful admin dashboard featuring localized interfaces, collapsible sidebar groups, and extensible widgets."
msgstr "AWCMS-Micro menyertakan dasbor admin canggih yang menampilkan antarmuka terlokalisasi, grup sidebar yang dapat diciutkan, dan widget yang dapat diperluas."

msgctxt "useCaseMobileHeading"
msgid "5. Mobile & IoT Backend"
msgstr "5. Backend Mobile & IoT"

msgctxt "useCaseMobileText"
msgid "Serve as a high-performance backend. Provide API endpoints with sub-millisecond response times, secure authentication, and real-time data sync."
msgstr "Berfungsi sebagai backend berkinerja tinggi. Sediakan endpoint API dengan waktu respons sub-milidetik, otentikasi aman, dan sinkronisasi data real-time."

msgctxt "useCaseAiHeading"
msgid "6. AI-Powered Workflows"
msgstr "6. Alur Kerja Bertenaga AI"

msgctxt "useCaseAiText"
msgid "Run intelligent agents, monitor logs, and trigger automated workflows based on database events and webhooks."
msgstr "Jalankan agen cerdas, pantau log, dan picu alur kerja otomatis berdasarkan event database dan webhook."

msgctxt "ctaTitle"
msgid "Ready to accelerate your next project?"
msgstr "Siap mempercepat proyek Anda berikutnya?"

msgctxt "ctaSubtitle"
msgid "Deploy AWCMS-Micro on Cloudflare Pages or run it locally in seconds. Join developers building resilient applications."
msgstr "Deploy AWCMS-Micro di Cloudflare Pages atau jalankan secara lokal dalam hitungan detik. Bergabunglah dengan pengembang yang membangun aplikasi tangguh."

